<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Avaliku teenistuse seaduse kehtivus prokur&ouml;ride suhtes </eesti>
<inglise>Application of Public Service Act in respect of prosecutors </inglise>
<eesti>Prokur&ouml;riteenistusele kohaldatakse avaliku teenistuse seadust (RT I 1995, 16, 228; 50, 764; 97, 1664; 1996, 15, 265; 45, 850; 1997, 1, 4; 29, 447; 1998, 34, 486; 38, 563; 41/42, 625; 50, 753; 57, 858; 110, 1809), kui k&auml;esolevast seadusest ei tulene teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>The Public Service Act (RT I 1995, 16, 228; 50, 764; 97, 1664; 1996, 15, 265; 45, 850; 1997, 1, 4; 29, 447; 1998, 34, 486; 38, 563; 41/42, 625; 50, 753; 57, 858; 110, 1809) applies to the prosecutors' service unless otherwise provided by this Act. </inglise>
