<eesti>Seaduslikkuse j&auml;relevalve kinnipidamiskohtades </eesti>
<inglise>Supervision of legality in penal institutions </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduslikkuse j&auml;relevalvet kinnipidamiskohtades teostab prokur&ouml;r, kellel on &otilde;igus: </eesti>
<inglise>The supervision of legality in penal institutions shall be exercised by a prosecutor who has the right to: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kontrollida igal ajal ja tingimusteta seaduste t&auml;itmist kinnipidamiskohtades ning tutvuda dokumentidega, mis on isiku kinnipidamiskohas viibimise v&otilde;i vahistamise aluseks; </eesti>
<inglise>1) monitor at any time and unconditionally compliance with the law in penal institutions and examine documents which are the basis for the imprisonment in a penal institution or taking into custody of a person; </inglise>
<eesti>2) vabastada viivitamatult seadusliku aluseta kinnipeetav isik; </eesti>
<inglise>2) release promptly a person who is in detention without legal basis; </inglise>
<eesti>3) k&uuml;sitleda kinnipidamiskohas viibivaid isikuid, v&otilde;tta neilt suulisi v&otilde;i kirjalikke seletusi." </eesti>
<inglise>3) question persons in penal institutions, and take oral and written explanations." </inglise>
